result.adr_address: 14 Second Street, Sai Ying Pun, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 14 Second Street, Sai Ying Pun, Hong Kong
result.name: Polygon Cafe

reviews.text: My favorite cafe around the area. The do beautiful latte arts. Not much things in the store: some seats, some pastries, 1 or 2 baristas, and that's all, and I think that's the best part of the cafe. Not much going on, just go there at around afternoon, get your favorite book, and enjoy the afternoon. The staffs are friendly as well. Their Flat white is pretty good. My go-to place if I want a good read in the afternoon.
Delicious food and drinks. Very nice service. I asked for a single shot latte cold with no ice. They were very caring to spare another shot for me in case the i think the drink's too milky.
Delicious coffee. Nice place too.

Quaint set up. Outdoors seating available but definitely not for summer.

Coffee is decent but personally found is too acidic to my liking.
The staff are not friendly. Even you got a good coffee...
